like":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:51:06.000Z","msg":"一介學生唔知有咩可以幫手，不過至少會推post"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:57:04.000Z","msg":"作爲學生，你嘅職責就係努力拓展自己嘅專長，長大成爲一個能夠貢獻香港，守護香港嘅優秀香港人。<br />\n每日起身提醒自己：香港唔可以再多一個親共嘅渣滓。"},{"pid":"b5137f411c5585913675797cdf804effc195f539","tid":1858334,"uid":13586,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:58:10.000Z","msg":"罷工喺香港從來唔係新事<br />\n省港大罷工，海員大罷工，葵涌貨櫃碼頭罷工，國泰罷工<br />\n<br />\n只係大型工會罷工係喺港豬嘅門檻同包袱莫名其妙地高<br />\n而且一直致力都冇一個政治形式嘅罷工，只有勞資糾紛嘅罷工<br />\n<br />\n而家正正就係一個以香港人，打工仔嘅健康為前提，武漢病毒漫延，政府無能，比8月5日更合情合理嘅一次罷工<br />\n<br />\n以後遊行示威抗爭嘅口號，除咗<br />\n「香港人！加油！」「香港人！反抗！」「香港人！報仇！」<br />\n更想多一句<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「香港人！罷工！」</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9afc56534e6e90d26537f7e2b5fcf137c877e5c3","tid":1858334,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"452b83920c605e13a09c33da526f608c70077cc0","tid":1858334,"uid":279090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:52:46.000Z","msg":"學生加1<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:58:40.000Z","msg":"你係香港嘅將來，香港嘅希望，香港嘅光。<br />\n努力成爲一個優秀嘅香港人，光復後嘅香港需要年青嘅人才接手。"},{"pid":"099a6c99666dd7108bf6e95b2a3598c031227983","tid":1858334,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:59:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8d1283e7499dd8dda3649fb4f96b7c3568b55c","tid":1858334,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fde6062ca6bf24e32187f889f9017e62ff8c4325","tid":1858334,"uid":131691,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"2c1a9dac3541331a8a2683be85b23f5292a3a65b","tid":1858334,"uid":300740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:51:06.000Z","m