amily."},{"pid":"31489c23aa82459f4e3c24cd5135642a6fc46abf","tid":1858334,"uid":59297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T16:11:01.000Z","msg":"不過依家街頭抗爭幫手真係難，始終疫症，大家就唯有一齊唔返工坐喺屋企<br />\n<br />\n唉我都驚醫護堅持唔到，一堅持唔到就露底牌，可能港共會由你罷兩三日"},{"pid":"1d5bfb5e0e935b9339f2940490398c2c129faaf5","tid":1858334,"uid":35301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T16:13:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"153427c261cdc183dcefd5fcee0ac25e04ea2206","tid":1858334,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T16:17:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"088904970f5e52a95bb516dfcdb7d577ff50270f","tid":1858334,"uid":218684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T16:19:53.000Z","msg":"Final year 學生<br />\n之前睇到d反送中新聞(721，831，雙11嗰d)，<br />\n就覺得自己好難對呢個世界有咩改變，<br />\n成日都好灰，好想了結自己。<br />\n<br />\n97年嘅我，就好似注定人生所有事都會好難完滿咁。<br />\n<br />\n依家，我希望自己可以從逆境中重新成長。<br />\n我前幾日生日，許咗個願望: 香港人可以重新掌握自己嘅未來。<br />\n<br />\n核爆都唔割，呢d bullshit，唔應該再講，我都無資格講。<br />\n如果無前線手足，恐怕我地嘅未來已經消亡。"},{"pid":"2e4af8a1897fe5f9aafa8512d5d47f5d9d25f0c8","tid":1858334,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T16:20:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9c97bfb85c6779bf3945a2f1e93564a65d5a2d7c","tid":1858334,"uid":27670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T16:21:58.000Z","msg":"推 背水一戰<br />\n不成功便成仁"},{"pid":"fc96e0ec92f0ccdc41cb138902b47c5b7154a907","tid":1858334,"uid":8745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T16:24:09.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\nbtw公司已經home office"},{"pid":"43160726c59d6fb4ec5f30d895455e22abebe485","tid":1858334,"uid":5050,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T16:27:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SXojGwO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSXojGwO.png&h=d064e9dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽日話比我知..我唔會做左香港人既Condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif